{"tid":1422500,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（非打手）未去睇獅子王o既手足，我建議你地去睇一次","createTime":"2019-08-06T11:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:34:28.000Z","uid":224836,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f04e124fe42552886ec924bc4f63f8136c3738","tid":1422500,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:01:46.000Z","msg":"我唔劇透<br />\n睇完既感想得一個<br />\n套戲既內容情節就係依加既香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位巴打睇完套戲之後 就會明點解我咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縱使97回歸比人入黎侵佔我地既地方 <br />\n22年黎我地選擇逃避 無面對過呢個事實既殘酷<br />\n依加2019年 我地身為土生土長既香港人 依加要去守護香港 拎番屬於我地既野 再次令香港呢個地方發光發亮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"073f19eb7bb401d61f41399397d0c97b5294657b","tid":1422500,"uid":253573,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"睇左 每次見到娜娜都想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d98dbae0232ee43b7553fc35854a351c3c137b9","tid":1422500,"uid":224836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"073f19eb7bb401d61f41399397d0c97b5294657b","tid":1422500,"uid":253573,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"睇左 每次見到娜娜都想笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你"},{"pid":"ff63b5320a3b8ed0c9b476ae33dd9ee5c08655eb","tid":1422500,"uid":205995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"我做開CD-ROM，但估唔到有人同我既諗法係一樣忍唔住要留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好記得辛巴呀媽(定佢女友娜娜話)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「呢度係我哋嘅屋企，我哋係唔會走嘅」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n即刻有淚光，明明